properties.areaDesc: Patuxent River to Broomes Island MD; Tidal Potomac from Key Bridge to Indian Head MD; Tidal Potomac from Indian Head to Cobb Island MD; Patapsco River including Baltimore Harbor
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 15 at 2:41PM EST until January 16 at 6:00PM EST by NWS Baltimore MD/Washington DC
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 35 kt
expected.

* WHERE...Tidal Potomac River from Key Bridge to Cobb Island MD,
Patapsco River including Baltimore Harbor, and Patuxent River
to Broomes Island MD.

* WHEN...From 9 AM to 6 PM EST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM TO 6 PM EST THURSDAY
